### Get all orders (AUTHENTICATED)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get order by ID (AUTHENTICATED)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get orders by status (AUTHENTICATED)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders/status/PENDING
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Update order status (AUTHENTICATED)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/orders/1/status?status=CONFIRMED
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Health check (PUBLIC)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/actuator/health